{"tid":234480,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人申請左TAFS之後退學冇還到","createTime":"2017-05-08T10:41:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-08T15:20:19.000Z","uid":77486,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"207a89b542881b20904cd508580d85fd10d389cb","tid":234480,"uid":77486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T10:41:28.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n<br />\n學資處批左全額比我<br />\n<br />\n之後我讀左一個sem就退左學<br />\n<br />\n咁淨係要還之後果兩個學期既錢<br />\n<br />\n但係我發夢用左筆錢<br />\n<br />\n本來想申請延遲還款<br />\n<br />\n但係屋企人資產果到過左個限額所以reject左<br />\n<br />\n咁小弟同屋企人關係唔好，老豆老母都唔肯比錢我還<br />\n<br />\n依家學資處話唔還就會交比律政司處理<br />\n<br />\n如果我每個月還1-2k會唔會比人起訴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n同埋交左比律政司處理會有咩後果<br />\n<br />\n我問學資處果個職員佢都話答唔到<br />\n<br />\n有冇巴打有呢啲經歷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d6e7367fd79ae91b4598da1771b7e98b9ed412b","tid":234480,"uid":72608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T10:54:40.000Z","msg":"告到破產<br />\n破產果幾年慘到仆街<br />\n以上9UP"},{"pid":"cadff0692eb29e6efd03844fc6f4484acc7aa7c4","tid":234480,"uid":77486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T10:58:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>告到破產<br />\n破產果幾年慘到仆街<br />\n以上9UP</blockquote><br />\n唔好嚇我啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e56edc3aecfab5f874ee8089143215b6e54b5801","tid":234480,"uid":35701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T12:00:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"963dde679e0269253512525a089567296542a868","tid":234480,"uid":41742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T12:01:39.000Z","msg":"發夢用左即係未用？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n還返d錢比人啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ba13282c1bfd1d0d42262512c8d00d18cb98740","tid":234480,"uid":6696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017